  "prompt": "What is the funniest incident that happened to your friends?",
  "response": "I don't have friends or personal experiences, but here's a funny story that often happens among friends:\n\nA group of friends decides to go out for dinner to a fancy restaurant. One of them, known for being a bit of a jokester, decides to play a harmless prank. While everyone is chatting and deciding what to order, he secretly switches the salt shaker with the sugar shaker. When their orders arrive, one friend goes to sprinkle what they think is salt on their pasta, only to find out it's sugar. The confused look on their face followed by the laughter from the group makes the evening memorable. The prankster quickly admits to the harmless switch, and they all have a good laugh about it, turning the mishap into an amusing story they'll recount for years.\n\nFeel free to share your own funniest incident with friends!",
